                  </div><div class="footer__block footer__block--text" ><p class="bold">Laykids Hakkında</p><div class="prose text-subdued"><p>Laykids, çocuk tekerlekli ayakkabı kategorisinde yenilikçi, kaliteli ve güvenilir ürünler sunan modern bir markadır. Çocukların özgürce hareket edebilmesi, eğlenirken kendilerini ifade edebilmesi ve her adımda özgüven kazanması için tasarlanır.</p></div></div></div><div class="footer__aside empty:hidden"><div class="footer__aside-bottom"><div class="footer__payment-icons h-stack wrap gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-labelledby="pi-american_express" viewBox="0 0 38 24" width="38" height="24"><title id="pi-american_express">American Express</title><path fill="#000" d="M35 0H3C1.3 0 0 1.3 0 3v18c0 1.7 1.4 3 3 3h32c1.7 0 3-1.3 3-3V3c0-1.7-1.4-3-3-3Z" opacity=".07"/><path fill="#006FCF" d="M35 1c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v18c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H3c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V3c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h32Z"/><path fill="#FFF" d="M22.012 19.936v-8.421L37 11.528v2.326l-1.732 1.852L37 17.573v2.375h-2.766l-1.47-1.622-1.46 1.628-9.292-.02Z"/><path fill="#006FCF" d="M23.013 19.012v-6.57h5.572v1.513h-3.768v1.028h3.678v1.488h-3.678v1.01h3.768v1.531h-5.572Z"/><path fill="#006FCF" d="m28.557 19.012 3.083-3.289-3.083-3.282h2.386l1.884 2.083 1.89-2.082H37v.051l-3.017 3.23L37 18.92v.093h-2.307l-1.917-2.103-1.898 2.104h-2.321Z"/><path fill="#FFF" d="M22.71 4.04h3.614l1.269 2.881V4.04h4.46l.77 2.159.771-2.159H37v8.421H19l3.71-8.421Z"/><path fill="#006FCF" d="m23.395 4.955-2.916 6.566h2l.55-1.315h2.98l.55 1.315h2.05l-2.904-6.566h-2.31Zm.25 3.777.875-2.09.873 2.09h-1.748Z"/><path fill="#006FCF" d="M28.581 11.52V4.953l2.811.01L32.84 9l1.456-4.046H37v6.565l-1.74.016v-4.51l-1.644 4.494h-1.59L30.35 7.01v4.51h-1.768Z"/></svg>
